<HL>
   Paxar Corp. Looks
   For Record Profit
   For Quarter, Year
   ----
   By Robin Goldwyn Blumenthal
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
02/14/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   PXR
</CO>
<MS>
INDUSTRIAL (IDU)
</MS>
<IN>
DOW JONES INTERVIEW (CEO)
